data.description: FULLY RENOVATED!  Welcome to this updated move-in-ready 4-bed, 1.75 bath home in Lakewood! Step inside into the light & bright space that can be used as a dining or living room with one of two cozy wood burning fireplaces the home offers. Gourmet kitchen with granite counters & stainless-steel appliances. Spacious family room with the second wood fireplace, large windows, & French doors to the backyard to allow abundance of natural light. Private primary bedroom with a gorgeous full bathroom. Three additional bedrooms & updated 3/4 bathroom with laundry complete this charming home. Enjoy the fully fenced yard with patio, perfect for entertaining. Two outdoor sheds allows for extra storage. Driveway for multiple cars and RV parking.
